                  </hi>. I am chief inspector of the Great Western Railway. The prisoner worked there, and received about 24<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. a-week—I produce the Act of Parliament constituting the company.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> Having a wife and family at home, literally starving, I cer<lb></lb>tainly did take them—I am very sorry for it.</p>
